\{ f_n \}
 \{ x : ( \max_{n \leq k} f_n) (x) > a \} = \bigcup_{n=1}^{k} \{ x : f_n(x) > a \} 
\max_{n\le k}f_n
\left(\max_{n\le k}f_n\right)(x)=\max_{n\le k}f_n(x)\;,
\left(\max_{n\le k}f_n\right)(x)>a
\max_{n\le k}f_n(x)>a
f_n(x)>a
n\le k
x\in\{y:f_n(y)>a\}
n\le k
